# Pinky & The Brain

Persistent cross-project AI memory system for AI coding assistants. Each project gets a companion .patb brain repo that stores decisions, pitfalls, conventions, and cross-project context.

```yaml
SKILL_URL: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yesitsfebreeze/pinky-and-the-brain/refs/heads/main/SKILL.md
PATB_URL: https://github.com/yesitsfebreeze/pinky-and-the-brain.patb
MAX_NOTES: 512
MIN_RATING: 300
DECAY_RATE: 1
PRUNE_THRESHOLD: 300
HIBERNATION_DAYS: 90
MAX_CONTEXT_NOTES: 8
MAX_CONTEXT_FILES: 5
MAX_LINKED_REPOS: 3
CONTEXT_DEPTH: 2
```
